'''埃爾莎·拉弗恩特·梅迪亞努'''（{{lang-en|Elsa Lafuente Medianu}}，{{bd|1976年|7月18日||}}），艺名'''埃爾莎·帕塔奇'''（{{lang-en|Elsa Pataky}}），西班牙模特、演員和電影製片人。在《[[玩命關頭5|玩命關頭5]]》、《[[玩命關頭6|玩命關頭6]]》和《[[玩命關頭7|玩命關頭7]]》及《[[玩命關頭8|玩命關頭8]]》中飾演艾琳娜·内維斯一角大獲好評而知名。她曾出演的電影有《[[航班蛇患|航班蛇患]]》、《[[鉛黄|鉛黄]]》、《[[偵探馬龍|偵探馬龍]]》和《[[迪迪好萊塢|迪迪好萊塢]]》。

== 早年 ==
埃尔莎·帕塔奇生于[[西班牙|西班牙]][[马德里|马德里]]<ref name=allmovie>{{cite web | url =  http://movies.nytimes.com/person/305590/Elsa-Pataky/biography | title =  Elsa Pataky | publisher =  All Movie Guide via ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' | accessdate =  2012-06-13 | archive-date =  2015-04-05 | archive-url =  https://web.archive.org/web/20150405145222/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/person/305590/Elsa-Pataky/biography | dead-url =  no }}</ref>，父亲何塞·弗朗西斯·拉弗恩特是西班牙的生物化学家，母亲克里斯蒂娜·帕塔奇·梅迪亚努是[[罗马尼亚人|罗马尼亚]]和[[匈牙利人|匈牙利]]混血的公关<ref name="yahoo">{{Cite web |url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1804504141/bio |title=Elsa Pataky Biography – Yahoo! Movies<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-04-11 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629001249/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1804504141/bio |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vogue.it/en/vogue-starscelebsmodels/vogue-stars/2010/06/elsa-pataky- |title=Elsa Pataky VIDEO Interview |work=Vogue |accessdate=21 June 2010 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716103418/http://www.vogue.it/en/vogue-starscelebsmodels/vogue-stars/2010/06/elsa-pataky- |archive-date=2011-07-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。帕塔奇毕业于[[圣巴布罗大学|圣巴布罗大学]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ceu.es/ |title=Universidad de San Pablo CEU Official site |publisher=Ceu.es |date= |accessdate=2012-03-14 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119100639/https://www.ceu.es/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主修新闻和表演。

== 私生活 ==
2006年起，帕塔奇与美国演员[[阿德里安·布罗迪|阿德里安·布罗迪]]约会<ref>{{cite web|author=Daily Mail Reporter|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1071395/The-19th-century-New-York-castle-romantic-film-star-Adrien-Brody-bought-fairytale-princess.html#ixzz2GN0ujzet|title=The 19th century New York castle romantic film star Adrien Brody bought his fairytale princess|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2008-10-07|accessdate=2012-12-28|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027101444/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1071395/The-19th-century-New-York-castle-romantic-film-star-Adrien-Brody-bought-fairytale-princess.html#ixzz2GN0ujzet|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年帕塔奇31岁生日时，布罗迪在纽约购置了一座19世纪的不动产，两人在纽约的房子于2008年10月被《HELLO!》以35页的篇幅公开<ref>{{cite web|author=Hello |url=http://www.helloonline.com/celebrities/2008/10/07/adrien-brody-hello!/|title=Adrien and Spanish love Elsa share their 'dream castle' with HELLO! |publisher=Hello magazine|date=2008-10-07 |accessdate=2012-12-28}}</ref>。两人于2009年分手，帕塔奇随后爱上法国演员[[奥利维·马丁内兹|奥利维·马丁内兹]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Marcy|url=http://www.zimbio.com/Adrien+Brody/articles/58/Adrien+Brody+Girlfriend+leaves+Olivier+Martinez|title=Adrien Brody’s Girlfriend leaves him for Olivier Martinez|publisher=Zimbio|date=2009-05-16|accessdate=2012-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090519125623/http://www.zimbio.com/Adrien+Brody/articles/58/Adrien+Brody+Girlfriend+leaves+Olivier+Martinez|archive-date=2009-05-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2010年初，帕塔奇开始与澳大利亚演员[[克里斯·海姆斯沃斯|克里斯·漢斯沃]]约会，在此之前双方各派代表进行约会<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/chris-hemsworths-wife-elsa-pataky-gives-birth-2012125 | title = Chris Hemsworth's Wife Elsa Pataky Gives Birth to Daughter India! | work = [[Us_Weekly|Us Weekly]] | date = 12 June 2012 | last = Macaluso | first = Beth Anne | accessdate = 28 December 2012 | archivedate = 2012-11-17 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6CFMOJwFV?url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/chris-hemsworths-wife-elsa-pataky-gives-birth-2012125 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。帕塔奇和克里斯·漢斯沃2010年圣诞假期期间结婚<ref>{{cite web|author=Julie Jordan|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20453412,00.html|title=Thor Star Chris Hemsworth Gets Married|publisher=People|date=2010-12-28|accessdate=2012-12-28|archive-date=2011-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110328091012/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20453412,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，育有三个孩子：女儿印第安·罗斯（2012年5月生）<ref>{{cite web |author=Macaluso, Beth Anne |url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/chris-hemsworths-wife-elsa-pataky-gives-birth-2012125 |title=Chris Hemsworth's Wife Elsa Pataky Gives Birth to Daughter India! |publisher=usmagazine.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-12 |archive-date=2015-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509001754/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/chris-hemsworths-wife-elsa-pataky-gives-birth-2012125 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和双胞胎儿子特里斯坦和萨沙（2014年3月生）<ref>{{cite web|last=Pataky|first=Elsa|title=Cómo he preparado la llegada de los bebés|url=http://blogs.glamour.es/elsa-pataky-confidential/como-he-preparado-la-llegada-de-los-bebes/|publisher=Glamour|accessdate=25 March 2014|language=es|archive-date=2015-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150503192501/http://blogs.glamour.es/elsa-pataky-confidential/como-he-preparado-la-llegada-de-los-bebes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://celebritybabies.people.com/2014/03/21/chris-hemsworth-elsa-pataky-welcome-twin-sons/|title=Chris Hemsworth and Elsa Pataky Welcome Twin Sons|first1=Tim|last1=Nudd|first2=Julie|last2=Jordan|date=21 March 2014|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|accessdate=21 March 2014|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321180219/http://celebritybabies.people.com/2014/03/21/chris-hemsworth-elsa-pataky-welcome-twin-sons/|archive-date=2014-03-21}}</ref>。

2012年9月，西班牙最高法院判处出版商艾迪西奥内斯·泽塔向帕塔奇赔偿31万欧元。2007年3月，该公司的《Interviu》杂志公布了用长镜头拍到的帕塔奇赤裸上身的照片，当时正为《[[Elle|Elle]]》杂志拍写真的帕塔奇正换衣服。泽塔集团对此表示上诉<ref>{{cite web|author1=Fiona Govan|title=Spanish actress Elsa Pataky wins topless photo case|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/spain/9550855/Spanish-actress-Elsa-Pataky-wins-topless-photo-case.html|publisher=Telegraph|accessdate=12 August 2014|date=18 September 2012|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516121733/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/spain/9550855/Spanish-actress-Elsa-Pataky-wins-topless-photo-case.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

除了[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]，她还精通[[英语|英语]]、[[罗马尼亚语|罗马尼亚语]]、[[意大利语|意大利语]]、[[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]和[[法语|法语]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.elsapataky.com/biografia/biografia.html |title=Elsa Pataky Biografia / Official Website |publisher=Elsapataky.com |date=2010-10-15 |accessdate=2012-03-14 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129034638/http://elsapataky.com/biografia/biografia.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

